  "text": "Embryos were incubated overnight in embryo culture media containing 0.15 mg/ml podophyllotoxin and 0.15 mg/ml vinblastine sulphate to induce cell cycle arrest [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Embryos were then incubated in 0.1% (w/v) hypotonic sodium citrate for 15 -20 min at room temperature before transfer to ice-cold 3:1 methanol:glacial acetic acid for 3 s before being spread on to a Superfrost Plus slide (VWR, Lutterworth, UK).",
